{
  "stem": "2373.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was not one tree, not a little grass-- nothing, only mud and dirt and dry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we really couldn't work it out where we are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then they told us, the old ones, that we are in Poland and that is Auschwitz and that they are crematoria.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they really said to us the first night, you see that fire there?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those are your parents are burning there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That's where the older prisoners who were jealous on the Hungarian ones, that we had it good until then.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were still at home, and they were suffering already for years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were just sitting around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And very interesting, we were cooking all the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were cooking and say recipes and what will we eat the first time when we come home and just--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you can call that food-- in the morning, we got such a brown liquid, which was supposed to be coffee or something, which in the beginning, we used for washing our hands and washing our face.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, we were drinking it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a little piece of bread-- bread, which was suppose to last you the whole day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people were cutting it to slices, and that's for lunch, that's for evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I, for myself, the minute I got it, I ate it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I [LAUGHS] didn't waste-- not a morsel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I ate everything straight away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- in the evening, we got such a grey-ish-- I don't know what it was, barley or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we made a point of it, that we are eating it just to keep up the strengths.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And to-- the-- the biggest problem was thirst.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no water at all-- not for washing, not for drinking.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
